Routes we will be analyzing are: Mumbai(BOM) Bengaluru(BLR) Delhi(DEL) Bengaluru(BLR) Delhi(DEL) Mumbai(BOM) Delhi(DEL) Kolkata(CCU) Delhi(DEL) Hyderabad (HYD)

Average Price per flight in route

In [26]:
matplotlib.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (30,20)
df_1_avg_price = df_1.groupby('FlightName')['Price'].mean().reset_index().astype({'Price':'int'}).sort_values(by='Price',ascending=False)
p = sns.barplot(x='FlightName',y='Price',data=df_1_avg_price)
p.bar_label(p.containers[0])
plt.title("Average Price per flight in route")
p.set_xticklabels(labels=df_1_avg_price["FlightName"], rotation=35)
sns.set(font_scale=1.25)
plt.show()

Insight

  • Indigo dominates the Indian aviation industry.
  • Spicejet has the least flight share in the country.
  • Flight fare is high during early morning and midnight time.
  • Vistara is the cosliest and Akasa is the cheapest airline in the country.
  • Cosliest flight route is the New Delhi - Bengaluru route.
